{"tid":2414240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好移民，一定要留係香港","createTime":"2021-02-19T09:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T11:23:23.000Z","uid":81236,"like":7,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8843cd4dc7d2291da1fb780f78a4d90fd6bbd8","tid":2414240,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:05:12.000Z","msg":"如果黃絲咁愛香港就唔好再走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為大家走左香港就唔再係香港<br />\n<br />\n無曬一班淨係得中國香港藉既人<br />\n<br />\n無曬一班真係為香港付出既人<br />\n<br />\n得返日後班補充人口既新香港<br />\n<br />\n個個都走曬有外國護照藍絲仲點去完外國返黎食住黃絲上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家好撚鍾意香港既真係唔好走<br />\n<br />\n你地走左藍絲第日食屎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n深藍人士上<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e48a043d16a3fa10c5f58021fc62da539c73a88","tid":2414240,"uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:05:50.000Z","msg":"愛港請留港<br />\n<br />\n別讓黃絲走了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604f802e234d15effdeeb162522f02df6bd16ad5","tid":2414240,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"黃絲走哂<br />\n<br />\n第日藍絲拎完外國護照返黎咪無得踩住人上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分分鐘新香港人地位更高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b40e3fbcbe6a28694dc7e6f7874a29d2f9ee34e","tid":2414240,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"香港之所以係香港,係因為有香港人嘅存在."},{"pid":"36a243508323f47b4240e25d85dbb54f8909002b","tid":2414240,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2b40e3fbcbe6a28694dc7e6f7874a29d2f9ee34e","tid":2414240,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"香港之所以係香港,係因為有香港人嘅存在."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:08:20.000Z","msg":"班黃絲走曬香港仲係咪香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以別讓黃絲走了"},{"pid":"3b5bd74850fab9f15374ec15fad154c60e28db46","tid":2414240,"uid":108016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"咁你走咗未？<br />\n<br />\n利申：Pr"},{"pid":"1c70d13c822a277696e69300fd4821b494618cad","tid":2414240,"uid":107419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:09:09.000Z","msg":"有咗國安法，無高度自治，無法治人權。<br />\n就算有黃絲，都已經唔係以前既香港。<br />\n走只係用腳投票，話比你共產黨聽我地唔會妥協。"},{"pid":"6050a871db5d93f6e659c96f3fe998332805258d","tid":2414240,"uid":358948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b40e3fbcbe6a28694dc7e6f7874a29d2f9ee34e","tid":2414240,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"香港之所以係香港,係因為有香港人嘅存在."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:09:29.000Z","msg":"香港之所以成為而家嘅香港，係因為有大量單程證落黎嘅新香港人嘅存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561a079ebeb8e89b390358a93ec6599fd4e37c8f","tid":2414240,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3b5bd74850fab9f15374ec15fad154c60e28db46","tid":2414240,"uid":108016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"咁你走咗未？<br />\n<br />\n利申：Pr"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd589122b026a435574176f44899eeb48ac217f","tid":2414240,"uid":107419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:10:23.000Z","msg":"Show blocked user 唔好放棄<br />\nPR狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db15ff77c2836217d25e048063777c56f96f0b5","tid":2414240,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6050a871db5d93f6e659c96f3fe998332805258d","tid":2414240,"uid":358948,"l